paragraphs.title: Age with Breaks
paragraphs.text:
/** %sql select chd, t.range , count(*) as count
from (
  select chd, case  
    when age between 0 and 15 then ' 0-15'
    when age between 16 and 25 then '16-25'
    when age between 26 and 45 then '26-45'
    else '46+' end as range
  from data) t
group by chd, t.range order by t.range **/

val exprAgeBreaks = expr("case when age between 0 and 15 then ' 0-15' when age between 16 and 25 then '16-25' when age between 26 and 45 then '26-45' else '46+' end")

val ageWithBreaks = data.withColumn("range", exprAgeBreaks)
                        .select('chd,'range)
                        .groupBy('chd,'range).count
                        .orderBy('range)

z.show(ageWithBreaks)

paragraphs.title: Tobacco with breaks
paragraphs.text:
/** %sql select chd, t.range, count(*) as count
from (
    select chd, case 
        when tobacco <= 0.05 then '1.low'
        when tobacco > 0.05 and tobacco > 2 then '2.high'
        else '3.very high' end as range
    from data ) as t
group by chd, t.range **/

val exprTobaccoBreaks = expr("case when tobacco <= 0.05 then '1.low' when tobacco > 0.05 and tobacco > 2 then '2.high' else '3.very high' end")

val tobaccoWithBreaks = data.withColumn("range", exprTobaccoBreaks)
                            .select('chd,'range)
                            .groupBy('chd,'range).count
                            .orderBy('range)

z.show(tobaccoWithBreaks)

paragraphs.title: Family History
paragraphs.text:
/** %sql select chd, famhist, count(*) as count
from data
group by chd, famhist order by chd **/

val famHistoryHist = data.groupBy('chd,'famhist).count.orderBy('famhist)
z.show(famHistoryHist)
